{
  "title": "Tempting Toasted Japanese Bananas Takoyaki",
  "description": "A funky and fluffy post-workout Japanese dish featuring fried ripe bananas in a takoyaki form, shio-cure, and low-calorie-friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
